Start Point: Thormac, outside the Abandoned Prison

Official Difficulty: Intermediate

Description: A member of the Thalmor, Thormac, has lost 3 domesticated Chaurus. Return them to him using his specialized capture spell.

Official length: Short

Requirements: None

Items required: None

Enemies to defeat: None

Quest Stages: 

Rewards: 1 level in One-Handed Training, a random magical staff

Note:
Locations - 
1. Olava the Feeble's house in Whiterun
2. Frostfruit Inn in Rorikstead
3. Temple of the Divines in Solitude
